nm:output.nm:control_stream:
$PROB RUN 3001; see nmtest_time_varying.R
$INPUT C ID TIME WT EVID AMT CMT SS II ADDL RATE LAGT MODE DUR2 RAT2 BIOAV DV
$DATA ../../data/3001.csv IGNORE=C
$SUBROUTINES ADVAN2 TRANS2
$PK
TVCL=THETA(1)*(WT/70)**0.75 CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1))
TVV2=THETA(2) V=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2))
TVKA=THETA(3) KA=TVKA*EXP(ETA(3))
$ERROR IPRED=A(2)/(V/1000) Y=IPRED*EXP(ERR(1))
CP = IPRED
$THETA (1.1, FIX) ;; CL (20, FIX) ;; V (1.5, FIX) ;; KA
$OMEGA 0.0 FIX 0.0 FIX 0.0 FIX
$SIGMA 0.00 FIX
$TABLE FILE=TAB ID TIME WT CL CP NOPRINT ONEHEADER NOAPPEND
$SIMULATION (2674474) ONLYSIMULATION
